itemDescription: British actor, writer, former professional quizzer and television personality

wikipedia_page.main: Connagh Joseph "C. J." de Mooi (pronounced [də moːi̯]; born Andrew Paul Booth on 5 November 1969) is a British actor, writer, former professional quizzer and television personality. He first appeared on television quiz show Eggheads in 2003, as one of five original members of the show's eponymous team.
